      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept car in good overall condition. It shows nicely inside and out, with a presentable exterior, a solid interior, and the kind of normal cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle rather than anything excessive. It\u2019s clearly been cared for, and a buyer should expect a dependable, above-average driver that doesn\u2019t need to be described as perfect to be appreciated. A very respectable example for someone looking for a nice car without paying mint-condition money.",
