      "description": "Affordable, no-nonsense transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone looking for a budget-friendly option, a project, or a practical backup car. Priced to move and presented with clear expectations, it offers an accessible entry point for anyone who wants usable transportation without a big upfront cost.",
