    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout or a great little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got plenty of life left for the right buyer and offers a budget-friendly way to get on the road. A sensible option for someone who values straightforward motoring, a bit of DIY potential, or just needs something cheap and usable. Priced to be a fair deal and sold with a friendly, honest approach.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid candidate for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. This car is in poor overall condition, but it still offers a stout platform with honest mechanical character and plenty of upside for a hands-on owner. The powertrain is serviceable, the chassis has usable bones, and it presents as a practical project, parts car, or budget commuter for the mechanically inclined. If you want an affordable entry point and don\u2019t mind putting in the work, this one has real potential.",
