      "description": "This car has the kind of personality you notice right away\u2014the sort of honest, road-worn machine that still carries stories in every panel and plenty of potential for its next chapter. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone looking for an inexpensive set of wheels, a hands-on project, or a practical daily driver with character you just don\u2019t get from newer cookie-cutter cars. If you appreciate a vehicle with grit, presence, and room to make it your own, this one offers a compelling opportunity at a budget-friendly price.",
